members..\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n\r\n# 31 Members attended the meeting..\r\n\r\n# It has been decided to help and support all the student\'s whose names were forwarded by School Principals.\r\nNames of Schools (all from Pauri Garhwal) &amp; nos of children\'s for support are:\r\n1. Adalikhal - 4 Nos.\r\n2. Khirerikhal - 6 Nos.\r\n3. Sald Mahadev - 3 Nos\r\n4. Dungri, Naini Danda - 3 Nos.\r\n\r\n# As we are also getting more and more names, so from next time onwards, we will give preference to those students who are:\r\n1. Girls\r\n2. Orphans\r\n3. Brilliant in Studies but whose parents can\'t support their studies\r\n\r\n# Governing Body was finalised as per below details:\r\n\r\n1. President : Shri Alok Vaishnav\r\n\r\n2. Vice President : Shri Kamal Dhyani\r\n\r\n3. General Secretary : Shri Jitender Lakhera\r\n\r\n4. Joint Secretary : Shri Pankaj Naithani\r\n\r\n5. Assistant Secretary : Shri Ashish Lakhera\r\n\r\n6. Treasure : Shri Surendra Lakhera &amp; Shri Rinkaj Kandwal\r\n\r\n# A Format for Membership Registration will be distributed to all the members soon. All members download the form fill up and handover same to Governing Body in next meeting.\r\n\r\n# Registering our Group as an Cooperative Society is in process and it will be completed soon.\r\n\r\n# Discussion on need for group of Volunteers, who can ask / verify the needy\'s details and can visit uttarakhand for giving doles in cash or kind will continue in our next meeting.\r\n\r\n# A Powerpoint presentation will be prepared for our group showing its background and working.\r\n\r\n# Means of Fund Collection were also discussed by way of selling Pahadi Dagdya Tshirts or from utlising the concept of Uttarakhand Fresh.\r\n\r\n# On the spot, Fund collection was Rs. 15,402\r\n\r\n# Our next meeting is fixed for 19th June, 2016 at same venue.\r\n\r\n# It has been agreed that we are very naive and can be seen a little unorganized but we are very determined to give back to our Devbhoomi Uttarakhand..\r\n\r\nWith the help, guidance &amp; suggestions from like minded people, gradually we will make our presence felt in Uttarakhand\r\n\r\n[ngg_images source=\"galleries\" container_ids=\"49\" display_type=\"photocrati-nextgen_basic_thumbnails\" override_thumbnail_settings=\"1\" thumbnail_width=\"240\" thumbnail_height=\"180\" thumbnail_crop=\"1\" images_per_page=\"10\" number_of_columns=\"0\" ajax_pagination=\"1\" show_all_in_lightbox=\"0\" use_imagebrowser_effect=\"1\" show_slideshow_link=\"1\" slideshow_link_text=\"MonthlyMeetingMay2016\" template=\"default\" slug=\"Monthly-Meeting-May-2016\" order_by=\"sortorder\" order_direction=\"ASC\" returns=\"included\" maximum_entity_count=\"500\"]</div>','Monthly Meeting 15 May 2016','','publish','closed','closed','','monthly-meeting-15-may-2016','','','2017-03-29 22:57:33','2017-03-29 17:27:33','',0,'http://pahadidagdya.com/?p=886',0,'post','',0),(887,1,'2017-03-29 22:54:41','0000-00-00 00:00:00','eyJpZF9maWVsZCI6IklEIiwiX19kZWZhdWx0c19zZXQiOnRydWV9','Untitled ngg_gallery','','draft','closed','closed','','mixin_nextgen_table_extras','','','2017-03-29 22:54:41','0000-00-00 00:00:00','eyJpZF9maWVsZCI6IklEIiwiX19kZWZhdWx0c19zZXQiOnRydWV9',0,'http://pahadidagdya.com/?p=887',0,'ngg_gallery','',0),(888,1,'2017-03-29 22:54:41','0000-00-00 00:00:00','eyJpZF9maWVsZCI6IklEIiwiX19kZWZhdWx0c19zZXQiOnRydWV9','Untitled ngg_pictures','','draft','closed','closed','','mixin_nextgen_table_extras','','','2017-03-29 22:54:41','0000-00-00 00:00:00','eyJpZF9maWVsZCI6IklEIiwiX19kZWZhdWx0c19zZXQiOnRydWV9',0,'http://pahadidagdya.com/?p=888',0,'ngg_pictures','',0),(889,0,'2017-04-30 22:42:22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','eyJpZF9maWVsZCI6IklEIiwiX19kZWZhdWx0c19zZXQiOnRydWV9','Untitled ngg_pictures','','draft','closed','closed','','mixin_nextgen_table_extras','','','2017-04-30 22:42:22','2017-04-30 17:12:22','eyJpZF9maWVsZCI6IklEIiwiX19kZWZhdWx0c19zZXQiOnRydWV9',0,'http://pahadidagdya.com/?p=889',0,'ngg_pictures','',0),(890,1,'2017-03-29 22:54:41'